04:06.480 --> 04:07.910
-=Judo athlete loses eyesight=-

04:07.910 --> 04:08.670
Go Du Yeong?

04:08.670 --> 04:10.240
Go Du Yeong?

04:10.250 --> 04:11.580
But,

04:11.580 --> 04:12.740
