live together.

08:36.010 --> 08:40.850
After that, I promise I'll 
disappear without a trace.

08:45.690 --> 08:48.350
<i>You rude jerk.</i>

08:48.360 --> 08:52.520
If a hyena comes into your 
home, you should at least 
come out to check.

08:57.030 --> 08:59.690
