something before she died.

09:11.380 --> 09:14.040
<i>By the way, don't expect
anything.</i>

09:14.050 --> 09:17.210
<i>Don't think I'm here to take
really good care of you!</i>

09:17.220 --> 09:19.380
<i>If you're having naive thoughts
like that,</i>

09:19.390 --> 09:22.720
<i>you should get rid of them as
soon as possible.</i>

10:05.100 --> 10:07.090
What was that?

10:14.780 --> 10:15.770
Hey.

10:15.780 --> 10:17.770
