do whatever you want.

10:54.650 --> 10:56.980
Give me one pack Lamborghini 
Ice Tornado.

10:56.990 --> 10:58.820
What?

10:58.820 --> 11:00.650
Lamborghini Ice Tor... Tor... 
That.

11:00.660 --> 11:01.640
Ajussi.

11:01.660 --> 11:04.150
One box Lamborghini menthol,
please.

11:04.160 --> 11:06.820
Ah, menthol.

11:06.830 --> 11:09.160
That's what I just said.

11:13.840 --> 11:15.170
Give me another one of those.

11:15.170 --> 11:17.160
They're sold out.

11:19.510 --> 11:21.170
Then that means...

11:21.180 --> 11:23.170
you should put it down.

11:23.180 --> 11:25.170
I already paid for it.

11:25.180 --> 11:26.670
Lamborghini menthol.

11:26.680 --> 11:28.840
I asked for it by its correct 
name,

11:28.850 --> 11:33.340
Lamborghini Ice Tornado, okay?

11:37.690 --> 11:39.350
Ajussi.

11:39.360 --> 11:41.020
Keep the change!

11:41.030 --> 11:42.520
Hey. Hey!

11:42.530 --> 11:43.860
Hey!

11:43.870 --> 11:45.860
Hey, you fucking bastard!

11:45.870 --> 11:47.700
- Give it to me. 
- Okay, okay.

11:47.700 --> 11:49.200
I'll give it to you. I'll give it 
to you.

11:51.710 --> 11:53.210
This bastard wants to die.

11:53.210 --> 11:54.700
Hey, you bastard.

11:54.710 --> 11:58.540
The next time we meet is the
day you die!

11:58.550 --> 12:00.710
Son of a bitch.

12:01.720 --> 12:02.880
Now my stomach hurts.

12:02.880 --> 12:04.220
What the hell?

12:04.220 --> 12:05.210
Why now?

12:05.220 --> 12:07.380
Damn, I really have to go.

12:07.390 --> 12:08.220
You're an asshole!

12:08.220 --> 12:11.220
You're just lucky I have to shit!

12:17.230 --> 12:19.720
Du Yeong, it's me. Su Hyun.

12:19.730 --> 12:22.730
Why don't you ever answer 
the phone?

12:24.070 --> 12:27.060
I'm at your front door right now.

12:27.080 --> 12:29.570
Are you at home...

12:32.250 --> 12:34.740
It opened.

12:36.250 --> 12:37.910
That hurts.

12:44.090 --> 12:46.750
Du Yeong.

12:53.600 --> 12:55.760
<i>Du Yeong.</i>

13:35.980 --> 13:36.970
Wh-Wh-Who are you?

13:36.980 --> 13:38.970
Who? Why did you hit me?

13:38.980 --> 13:41.810
What the heck?

13:41.820 --> 13:45.310
So what is your relationship?
Are you his girlfriend?

13:45.320 --> 13:47.310
It looks like Du Yeong won't
eat anything.

13:47.320 --> 13:48.650
He'll eat when he gets hungry.

13:48.660 --> 13:52.150
He's not a child.

13:52.160 --> 13:53.650
Don't talk about him like that!

13:53.660 --> 13:57.830
Why are you shouting at me,
woman?

14:01.340 --> 14:02.830
Du Yeong, let's eat.

14:02.840 --> 14:05.000
What is that woman doing?

14:05.010 --> 14:05.840
<i>Du Yeong.</i>

14:05.840 --> 14:08.000
<i>Du Yeong, get up. Let's eat...</i>

14:08.010 --> 14:10.340
<i>Du Yeong, what's wrong?</i>

14:10.350 --> 14:13.180
<i>Du Yeong, open your eyes!</i>

14:18.690 --> 14:20.520
Listen carefully.

14:20.520 --> 14:23.350
I didn't come here to pay my 
last respects to you.

14:23.360 --> 14:24.850
Don't make a big fuss.

14:24.860 --> 14:28.350
If you really want to die, 
then die quietly.

14:28.360 --> 14:31.360
Otherwise, eat and stay alive.

14:47.720 --> 14:49.050
He said it's malnutrition.

14:49.050 --> 14:52.880
Does malnutrition make any 
sense?

14:52.890 --> 14:54.720
Do you think it only takes 
ability to be a national athlete?

14:54.720 --> 14:56.220
A national athlete also needs
stamina.

14:56.220 --> 14:58.560
Shouldn't you at least pay
attention whether he eats or not?

14:58.560 --> 15:00.550
Then take him away.

15:00.560 --> 15:02.720
Since you're so worried, 
just take him.

15:02.730 --> 15:05.560
