a national athlete.

15:08.900 --> 15:11.060
That should do well.

15:11.070 --> 15:13.400
Are you trash?

15:19.750 --> 15:22.240
Because of that damn kid, my 
life really has become a pile 
of trash.

15:22.250 --> 15:24.740
- Fucking seriously.
- Fucking seriously?

15:24.750 --> 15:25.910
For patient Go Du Yeong,

15:25.920 --> 15:28.080
