16:22.810 --> 16:25.300
Is it fried ham?

16:35.660 --> 16:37.320
It's Spam.

16:38.660 --> 16:40.650
This jerk is too much.

16:42.000 --> 16:44.490
Your eyes don't work and now
even your nose is broken?

16:44.500 --> 16:46.160
No way is it Spam. 
[lunch meat brand]

16:46.170 --> 16:49.160
Your entire existence is spam, 
kid. 
["junk email"]

16:52.010 --> 16:54.170
Also,

16:54.180 --> 16:58.340
you should be grateful I'm a
humanitarian.

16:58.350 --> 17:01.340
