is rice to stuff into your mouth.

17:01.350 --> 17:02.510
Ramen is rice now?

17:02.520 --> 17:04.180
Are you disrespecting ramen?

17:04.190 --> 17:05.520
Shin Ramyeon, Neoguri,

17:05.520 --> 17:07.680
Haemul Ramyeon, Nagasaki...

17:07.690 --> 17:10.849
So many varieties, you 
dumb ass.

17:10.859 --> 17:12.190
What about you?

17:12.190 --> 17:15.530
You grew up eating well, so it 
won't hurt you to eat this for 
10 more years.

17:15.530 --> 17:18.020
So just shut up and eat.

17:18.200 --> 17:21.030
