17:25.710 --> 17:27.869
Are you wearing cologne?

17:27.880 --> 17:29.540
"You?" 
[not honorifics]

17:29.540 --> 17:31.880
"You?"

17:31.880 --> 17:33.540
You son of a bitch, that's not
how you talk to your brother.

17:33.550 --> 17:35.040
Then calling me "son of a bitch"
is okay?

17:35.050 --> 17:37.380
You son of a bitch!

17:37.390 --> 17:38.370
Ow.

17:38.390 --> 17:40.220
Your mouth...

17:40.220 --> 17:41.710
I guess it still works, huh?

17:41.720 --> 17:44.710
It would be nice if that didn't
work, either.

17:50.400 --> 17:52.730
You ruined my appetite.

18:09.420 --> 18:10.580
You...

18:10.590 --> 18:12.080
asshole.

18:12.090 --> 18:13.920
Can you see?

18:13.920 --> 18:16.580
You can see a little bit, right?
You son of a bitch.

18:16.590 --> 18:18.750
Some humanitarian.

18:18.760 --> 18:21.420
Just a thug.

18:23.930 --> 18:25.090
Hey!

18:25.100 --> 18:26.090
What, asshole?

18:26.100 --> 18:28.760
What? What? Asshole.

18:29.770 --> 18:31.600
Son of a bitch.

18:33.770 --> 18:35.770
That hurts.

18:38.950 --> 18:40.780
I'm sorry, Customer.

18:40.780 --> 18:44.440
