His older brother.

18:56.300 --> 18:59.130
We're family...

18:59.130 --> 19:01.120
Seriously.

19:11.810 --> 19:14.140
Oh, squid strips.

19:14.150 --> 19:15.140
Ajussi.

19:15.150 --> 19:16.310
