19:16.320 --> 19:19.150
Oh, here it is.

19:19.150 --> 19:21.140
This much, right?

19:22.820 --> 19:23.810
Add this on.

19:23.820 --> 19:25.820
Where did my cola go?

19:28.330 --> 19:29.820
Damn it!

19:29.830 --> 19:32.320
Hey, hey, hey!

19:32.330 --> 19:33.990
