19:41.010 --> 19:42.670
So, well...

19:42.680 --> 19:45.010
You live in this neighborhood?

19:46.010 --> 19:46.840
What if I do?

19:46.850 --> 19:48.180
Then...

19:48.180 --> 19:52.020
Let's make a rule.

19:52.020 --> 19:55.510
Whoever pays for it, gets it.
Okay?

19:55.520 --> 19:59.360
What kind of work do you do?

19:59.360 --> 20:02.190
