20:02.200 --> 20:05.860
What do you think I do?

20:05.870 --> 20:08.360
I-I didn't ask.

20:08.370 --> 20:09.700
I'm not interested.

20:09.700 --> 20:10.690
What are you talking about?

20:10.710 --> 20:12.540
That means go figure it out
yourself,

20:12.540 --> 20:14.030
old man.

20:14.040 --> 20:16.030
Give me my cola!

20:16.040 --> 20:17.540
Omo. What to do?

20:17.550 --> 20:20.210
I'm sorry. Your suit. Aigoo.

20:20.210 --> 20:21.370
It's time to light the incense.
[funeral ceremony]

20:21.380 --> 20:22.540
Light the incense!

20:22.550 --> 20:24.380
Don't be like this!

20:24.390 --> 20:25.550
Don't chase me! Don't chase me!

20:25.550 --> 20:27.380
You're the neighborhood 
nutjob!

20:27.390 --> 20:31.050
The next time I see you, you
asshole, your mother will be 
burning incense!

20:31.060 --> 20:33.890
