pork, right?

20:44.740 --> 20:46.230
Sweet and sour pork. Here.

20:46.240 --> 20:48.570
Have a bite. Open up.

20:48.580 --> 20:49.410
What are you doing?

20:49.410 --> 20:51.070
What do you think?

20:51.080 --> 20:52.740
