20:52.750 --> 20:56.910
It really makes me feel bad.

20:58.420 --> 21:00.080
A fork would be better, right?

21:00.090 --> 21:01.750
Wait a second.

21:05.260 --> 21:06.760
Okay, here's a fork.

21:06.760 --> 21:08.920
Here's a fork. Here's a fork.

21:10.600 --> 21:12.260
Here. Say "ah".

21:23.280 --> 21:25.270
