21:28.450 --> 21:30.610
Here, it's in front of you.

21:32.950 --> 21:36.290
That's a carrot.

21:36.290 --> 21:37.790
That's cucumber. Cucumber.

21:37.790 --> 21:39.950
Cucumber.

21:39.960 --> 21:40.790
Left. Left.

21:40.800 --> 21:42.290
I'm not eating.

21:53.970 --> 21:55.480
I'll just stab it for you.

21:55.480 --> 21:57.470
Eat.

22:03.820 --> 22:07.980
It's good. It's good, right?

22:07.990 --> 22:09.820
It must be good!

22:09.820 --> 22:11.160
I told you so.

22:11.160 --> 22:13.650
Okay! How about the black
bean noodles?

22:13.660 --> 22:15.490
