22:15.500 --> 22:17.490
You know you have to eat it 
before it gets too mushy.

22:17.500 --> 22:19.490
Here, dig in.

22:30.010 --> 22:33.340
Wow! You eat well, little
brother!

22:33.350 --> 22:36.180
You can really eat.

22:36.180 --> 22:38.520
This is from Yangjagang, right?

22:38.520 --> 22:41.680
Yangjagang?

22:41.690 --> 22:43.350
Are you a ghost?
[how did you know?]

22:43.360 --> 22:44.520
You are a ghost.

22:44.530 --> 22:48.190
Wow, you're really amazing.

22:48.200 --> 22:50.860
By the way...

22:52.530 --> 22:55.700
Our father and your mom,

22:55.700 --> 23:00.040
that columbarium said they
want to move their ashes.

23:00.040 --> 23:02.370
Because of that...

23:02.380 --> 23:03.710
we need to submit some 
documents.

23:03.710 --> 23:06.040
I can't sign by myself, since
you're also their child.

23:06.050 --> 23:07.210
So I need a...

23:07.210 --> 23:08.040
is it power of attorney?

23:08.050 --> 23:11.040
They said I need to bring that.

23:11.050 --> 23:12.710
Anyway, it's a big hassle.

23:12.720 --> 23:14.550
I guess just to do something
so small,

23:14.560 --> 23:17.220
the procedures are still very
complicated.

23:17.220 --> 23:19.220
So?

23:21.230 --> 23:24.060
Where is your seal?

23:24.060 --> 23:28.230
Why does the columbarium need 
my seal to move their ashes?

23:29.570 --> 23:31.900
What do you mean, you 
bastard?

23:31.910 --> 23:32.900
Looking at your reaction just now,

23:32.910 --> 23:37.570
you must think I'm going to
do something dishonest, 
is that it?

23:37.580 --> 23:41.410
Wow, I'm really disappointed!
Seriously.

23:41.420 --> 23:42.750
Wow.

23:42.750 --> 23:43.580
Hey...

23:43.580 --> 23:47.420
No matter what you think, why
would I use your seal like that?

23:47.420 --> 23:49.250
Just forget it then!

23:49.260 --> 23:50.760
We'll just let them take those
two old people's ashes,

23:50.760 --> 23:55.250
and sprinkle them in the 
Yangjaecheon stream.

23:55.260 --> 23:57.250
What I said,

23:57.260 --> 24:00.260
I didn't mean it like that.

24:07.610 --> 24:09.770
Please confirm it.

24:12.280 --> 24:15.110
It's perfect.

24:16.120 --> 24:17.280
Thank you.

24:17.280 --> 24:19.280
You've worked hard.

24:21.620 --> 24:25.110
It's under 3000 cc, so it has 
the best fuel economy.

24:25.130 --> 24:27.120
Take a look.

24:27.130 --> 24:29.290
This opens!

24:29.300 --> 24:32.290
This, there's this. It should be
able to open, right?

24:32.300 --> 24:33.630
First time in a car like this?

24:33.630 --> 24:38.130
So for this one, how much is it?

24:38.140 --> 24:40.130
Just a moment.

24:42.310 --> 24:44.140
You give a discount for the
disabled, right?

24:44.140 --> 24:46.140
What?

24:48.820 --> 24:51.980
Try it. A macaroon.

24:58.490 --> 25:00.650
Guess where I bought them.

25:00.660 --> 25:03.150
Icheon-dong.

25:03.160 --> 25:04.990
They're good, right?

25:05.000 --> 25:07.830
Those are your favorites.

25:10.170 --> 25:12.660
Du Yeong.

25:12.670 --> 25:15.670
Judo... keep practicing.

25:15.680 --> 25:18.510
I can't see anything, so how 
can I practice judo?

25:18.510 --> 25:20.010
Don't misunderstand and just
listen to me first.

25:20.010 --> 25:22.350
I've been checking into...

25:22.350 --> 25:25.340
the Paralympic national team.

25:31.690 --> 25:33.020
If you get selected,

25:33.030 --> 25:35.520
you will be able to...

25:37.360 --> 25:40.530
I've lived in this house for 
20 years,

25:40.530 --> 25:43.200
but I can't even find my 
own room.

25:43.200 --> 25:46.700
You want me to keep practicing
judo?

25:46.710 --> 25:50.040
What do you think that's called?

25:52.050 --> 25:54.710
That's called disability 
overconfidence.

26:39.930 --> 26:42.420
My temple.

26:46.600 --> 26:50.430
<i>No, no. You can't drink that.</i>

26:50.440 --> 26:52.100
The best kind of beauty

26:52.110 --> 26:54.770
is dumb beauty.

27:01.280 --> 27:02.110
Your shoes are loud.

27:02.120 --> 27:03.950
Oppa...

27:03.950 --> 27:07.440
this is your house?

27:07.450 --> 27:08.790
You're so cute, so cute.

27:08.790 --> 27:10.950
Our house has a mad dog.

27:10.960 --> 27:12.290
It will be noisy if you wake it.

27:12.290 --> 27:14.620
Just take my hand quietly.

27:14.630 --> 27:17.120
Talk softly.

27:22.800 --> 27:25.290
This way, this way.

27:27.640 --> 27:30.300
Oppa! A ghost, a ghost!

27:30.310 --> 27:32.640
You're sitting here?

27:32.650 --> 27:33.640
Oppa.

27:33.650 --> 27:35.980
The mad dog is a man?

27:35.980 --> 27:37.640
A mad dog?

27:37.650 --> 27:39.310
I meant that...

27:39.320 --> 27:40.820
No.

27:40.820 --> 27:42.310
It's not like that.

27:42.320 --> 27:46.160
Before this mad dog bites you,
you'd better get out of here.

27:46.160 --> 27:48.150
This kid, talking to your 
brother like that.

27:48.160 --> 27:49.150
Who do you think...

27:49.160 --> 27:52.330
Hey, hey, hey.

27:52.330 --> 27:54.160
Where are you going? Cutie!

27:54.170 --> 27:55.500
Hey, Baby!

27:59.510 --> 28:01.500
Bastard.

28:01.510 --> 28:05.170
People should have at least
some common sense.

28:05.180 --> 28:09.340
If you have common sense, you
don't need education, money or
whatever. Fuck.

28:09.350 --> 28:12.180
Just because you're fucking
disabled, I'm screwed.

28:12.190 --> 28:14.350
I was trying to be a good
example for you, you fucker.

28:14.350 --> 28:18.350
Then you turn on me like that?
So damn annoying.

28:18.860 --> 28:20.190
Gui-dong Community Center.

28:20.190 --> 28:22.030
Who are you talking to?

28:22.030 --> 28:25.190
Yes, hello. You came to my
house the other day.

28:25.200 --> 28:26.360
This is Go Du Yeong.

28:26.370 --> 28:29.860
You asked me if I would be 
interested in rehabilitation.

28:29.870 --> 28:30.860
I've been thinking about it.

28:30.870 --> 28:33.860
Compared to how I am now, it
would probably be good for me.

28:33.870 --> 28:36.710
I'm curious about something.

28:36.710 --> 28:38.870
If a criminal was given parole
just to take care of me,

28:38.880 --> 28:41.540
will he be sent back to prison?

28:41.550 --> 28:43.710
He doesn't help me at all.

28:43.720 --> 28:44.710
You crazy bastard.

28:44.720 --> 28:46.050
Are you an insane asshole?

28:46.050 --> 28:48.540
You're driving me crazy!

28:48.560 --> 28:50.890
I was doing fine without you.

28:50.890 --> 28:53.220
Please get the hell out.

29:01.900 --> 29:04.060
That jerk just had a temper
tantrum.

29:08.080 --> 29:10.410
Hello?

29:12.080 --> 29:14.240
Du Yeong is wasting his ability.

29:14.250 --> 29:17.740
In the Paralympics, at least he 
would still be involved in sports.

29:17.750 --> 29:19.940
As his brother, explain that
to him.

29:21.260 --> 29:23.590
He said he doesn't want to, 
so why should I?

29:23.590 --> 29:26.580
That's why you need to 
persuade him!

29:26.590 --> 29:28.930
You live together, so keep 
encouraging him.

29:28.930 --> 29:31.260
I don't have that much free time.

29:31.270 --> 29:33.600
You must be a gangster.

29:33.600 --> 29:36.090
What?

29:36.100 --> 29:38.260
As his brother, your car is 
pretty fancy.

29:38.270 --> 29:39.760
Where did you get the money
to buy it?

29:39.770 --> 29:41.270
You even put Du Yeong's 
disabled person sticker on it.

29:41.280 --> 29:44.440
Someone who's so busy has 
time to take care of all of that?

29:47.610 --> 29:49.120
I think you're interested in me.

29:49.120 --> 29:50.450
I don't care about sports.

29:50.450 --> 29:51.110
Are you out of your mind?

29:51.120 --> 29:53.110
Then why don't you mind your
own business?

29:53.120 --> 29:55.280
He's so scared, he doesn't dare
step outside.

29:55.290 --> 29:58.120
You're not his full brother, 
but this is still outrageous.

29:58.130 --> 29:59.290
You're still his older brother.

29:59.290 --> 30:00.120
As an older brother, you...

30:00.130 --> 30:03.120
If you're giving out advice, 
I have something else to do.

30:03.130 --> 30:05.460
There are plenty of families who
get along without blood ties.

30:05.470 --> 30:07.960
Family members, my ass.

30:11.470 --> 30:14.460
Maybe that child was bored, 
so he played a little joke.

30:14.470 --> 30:15.810
No matter how well I treat him,

30:15.810 --> 30:19.800
I can't erase the psychological
trauma he suffered.

30:19.810 --> 30:23.310
Go Du Yeong, are you eating
properly?

30:23.320 --> 30:24.650
Shin Ramyeon.

30:24.650 --> 30:26.810
Neoguri.

30:26.820 --> 30:27.810
Nagasaki.

30:28.820 --> 30:31.990
When he was alone, he couldn't
even cook ramen.

30:31.990 --> 30:34.830
I saw him breaking up and 
eating the dry noodles.

30:36.000 --> 30:39.660
He begged me to cook every 
brand for him. Here's a drink.

30:39.670 --> 30:42.330
If you have difficulty with meals, 
you can apply for assistance.

30:42.340 --> 30:45.170
We can provide kimchi and 
other side dishes for support.

30:45.170 --> 30:47.160
You're doing good work.

30:47.170 --> 30:48.330
Your younger brother,

30:48.340 --> 30:52.180
because of the change in his 
situation may possibly develop
depression.

30:53.180 --> 30:54.670
With you by his side,

30:54.680 --> 30:57.510
it would be good for you to 
accompany him on walks.

30:57.520 --> 31:00.180
Enjoy being in the sunshine.

31:02.190 --> 31:03.850
I'm going in.

31:03.860 --> 31:06.020
Sit out here in the sun, kid.

31:06.030 --> 31:07.360
She said you have depression.

31:07.360 --> 31:09.520
I'm depressed because of you.

31:09.530 --> 31:11.860
And you really piss me off too!

31:11.870 --> 31:14.700
Prison or family, it's all the 
same. Fuck it.

31:35.890 --> 31:37.720
Don't you have...

31:37.720 --> 31:39.560
anyplace you want to go?

31:39.560 --> 31:42.050
Didn't you say the columbarium 
moved?

31:43.060 --> 31:45.730
I want to go there.

31:48.740 --> 31:51.400
You want to go there with me?

31:51.410 --> 31:53.570
You and me?

31:53.570 --> 31:56.060
We're so close, right?

31:56.080 --> 31:57.740
Those genes were heartless.

31:57.740 --> 31:59.740
You're fine. Your mother was
also fine.

31:59.750 --> 32:02.410
If you don't want to, then forget
it. Stop bitching about it.

32:02.420 --> 32:05.910
Shut up, asshole.

32:26.610 --> 32:29.440
Do you remember?

32:29.440 --> 32:31.600
The Jongsu public baths.

32:31.610 --> 32:34.100
In Yangjagang?

32:34.110 --> 32:37.110
When dad got paid,

32:37.120 --> 32:39.450
mom and dad,

32:39.450 --> 32:41.610
you and me,

32:41.620 --> 32:43.450
would bathe there.

32:43.460 --> 32:45.120
Then we'd eat black bean 
noodles.

32:45.130 --> 32:47.620
I don't remember.

32:47.630 --> 32:51.620
After you left, we never went
again.

32:51.630 --> 32:53.960
When I kept pestering him to go,

32:53.970 --> 32:56.300
<i>he said we had to wait until 
you came back.</i>

32:56.300 --> 32:58.290
What are you talking about?

32:58.310 --> 33:03.470
You think we all lived happily
after you left, don't you?

33:03.480 --> 33:07.640
Maybe it was because you
were an adolescent.

33:07.650 --> 33:11.480
Maybe you wanted to be a 
success before you came back.

33:11.490 --> 33:14.820
I dreamed up every kind of 
excuse to understand you.

33:14.820 --> 33:18.310
But you still never came back.

33:19.990 --> 33:24.990
At 18 years old, I had to handle
my parents' funeral all alone.

33:26.330 --> 33:29.830
<i>That's when I gave up.</i>

33:29.840 --> 33:33.330
<i>Our relationship was really over.</i>

33:46.190 --> 33:49.520
I won't report you to the prison, 
so don't worry.

33:49.520 --> 33:51.860
You can leave easily.

33:51.860 --> 33:54.520
By now, I can take care of 
myself.

34:10.210 --> 34:12.540
Get up.

34:12.550 --> 34:14.540
Hey, get up.

34:17.219 --> 34:19.550
I said get up, you jerk.

34:19.550 --> 34:20.540
What are you doing?

34:20.550 --> 34:22.389
Get up.

34:22.389 --> 34:24.350
- Come on, up.
- Quit!

34:24.560 --> 34:25.889
Get up now.

34:25.889 --> 34:27.550
This damn kid.

34:27.560 --> 34:30.050
Do as you're told. Get up.

34:30.060 --> 34:32.050
Get up.

34:32.070 --> 34:33.230
Damn it!

34:33.230 --> 34:35.560
I was going to take you to the
sauna, you jerk.

34:35.570 --> 34:36.560
To wash...

34:36.570 --> 34:39.570
Soak for a while, kid.

34:41.070 --> 34:47.070
Go Du Yeong's layer of dead 
skin from the past 10 years 
must be unbelievable.

34:48.250 --> 34:49.580
No.

34:49.580 --> 34:51.239
I want to go back home.

34:51.250 --> 34:53.909
You said you wanted to come.

34:53.920 --> 34:56.250
Since we're here, just get 
a scrub.

34:56.260 --> 34:58.250
Hurry and undress.

35:10.940 --> 35:12.100
You grew up pretty well.

35:12.110 --> 35:13.770
What are you doing?

35:14.440 --> 35:15.770
Crazy jerk.

35:15.780 --> 35:18.610
You really do see a little,
you asshole.

35:18.610 --> 35:22.100
It's obvious you can see.

35:22.120 --> 35:25.610
Wow, that jerk.

35:28.460 --> 35:30.450
Wow, look at all this dead skin!

35:30.460 --> 35:32.450
It will probably clog the drain.

35:32.460 --> 35:34.450
Just be quiet and scrub.

35:34.460 --> 35:36.450
This is cool, right?

35:36.460 --> 35:39.300
Can't you tell I'm an expert?

35:39.300 --> 35:42.460
Did you just eat and scrub 
backs?

35:42.470 --> 35:43.960
Kid,

35:43.970 --> 35:45.470
before I went to prison,

35:45.470 --> 35:47.630
I hid inside a public bath for 
a year.

35:47.640 --> 35:50.970
I helped scrub people's backs
for a whole year.

35:50.980 --> 35:54.810
That's how a jerk who ran away
from home was able to live.

35:54.810 --> 35:57.810
I was a waiter, porter, even a
beauty salon assistant,

35:57.820 --> 35:59.810
just to get a mouthful of food.

36:02.990 --> 36:05.980
Then why did you run away 
from home?

36:08.330 --> 36:11.320
Your brain is useless if you
don't understand.

36:11.330 --> 36:14.490
My mom and you didn't get
along, right?

36:17.840 --> 36:20.170
Your mom treated me very well.

36:20.170 --> 36:22.660
After your mother walked in
the door,

36:22.680 --> 36:24.670
I had the best lunch in my 
whole class.

36:24.680 --> 36:26.510
At lunch time,

36:26.510 --> 36:29.000
the moms would arrive with
udong noodles.

36:29.020 --> 36:31.680
your mom was usually first.

36:31.690 --> 36:33.850
I still remember what she 
sent me.

36:33.850 --> 36:36.010
But,

36:36.020 --> 36:39.190
one day the ajumma who 
lived next door

36:39.190 --> 36:41.180
came over and talked to me.

36:41.190 --> 36:43.360
She woke me up.

36:43.360 --> 36:45.700
She said how could I be so
stupid?

36:45.700 --> 36:47.690
Why?

36:50.200 --> 36:52.870
Why?

36:52.870 --> 36:55.710
She said, "That woman that 
you call mother. That woman..."

36:55.710 --> 36:58.370
"is the woman who nursed your
mom before she died."

36:58.380 --> 37:00.210
She said if my mom looked 
down from heaven,

37:00.210 --> 37:02.040
she would probably feel she
died unfairly and hate me.

37:02.050 --> 37:04.710
So, I got fucking angry and 
ran away, why?

37:04.720 --> 37:08.710
The two of them had been 
praying for my mother's early 
death.

37:08.720 --> 37:12.390
That's what I thought, kid.

37:12.390 --> 37:14.050
Why did you ask that?

37:14.060 --> 37:16.890
You pulled out my dark
secret.

37:24.570 --> 37:26.730
Scrub in a different place!

37:26.740 --> 37:29.400
It looks like I'm using an 
eraser on your back!

37:29.410 --> 37:33.400
No matter how much I scrub, 
the dead skin doesn't stop.

37:33.410 --> 37:34.740
I'm probably bleeding by now.

37:34.750 --> 37:36.080
Seriously, kid.

37:36.080 --> 37:37.580
My hands will bleed from
scrubbing you.

37:37.580 --> 37:39.920
There's so much.

37:41.760 --> 37:44.420
What's this back?

37:44.420 --> 37:48.090
How did it get so broad? 
You used to be a little shrimp.

37:48.090 --> 37:50.430
That "pepper" didn't have a
single hair.
[penis]

37:50.430 --> 37:54.420
Now it's already filled in 
thick and black.

37:56.770 --> 37:58.600
No good.

37:58.610 --> 38:00.270
Let's go.

38:00.270 --> 38:01.260
I have plenty.

38:01.270 --> 38:03.270
You have a lot of sportswear.

38:03.280 --> 38:05.940
A man's clothing is important,
kid.

38:08.950 --> 38:09.940
Du Yeong.

38:09.950 --> 38:11.280
Are you okay?

38:11.280 --> 38:14.120
He shouldn't be standing in
the road.

38:14.120 --> 38:18.110
Wait, wait, wait.

38:18.120 --> 38:19.960
What are you doing?

38:19.960 --> 38:21.460
What?

38:21.460 --> 38:22.120
Me?

38:22.130 --> 38:24.290
Yes, you.

38:24.300 --> 38:26.130
It's obvious. I'm shopping.

38:26.130 --> 38:28.120
Who do you think you are?

38:28.130 --> 38:31.470
If you knock over a blind person, 
shouldn't you apologize?

38:34.640 --> 38:35.630
Blind person?

38:35.640 --> 38:37.970
If he's blind, where's his 
walking stick?

38:37.980 --> 38:39.970
Why does he go out without a
stick just to cause problems?

38:39.980 --> 38:42.640
I mean, when you come across
a disabled person, just be kind.

38:42.650 --> 38:44.140
Shouldn't you have that 
basic humanity?

38:44.150 --> 38:46.810
That's really annoying.

38:48.660 --> 38:50.150
This jerk.

38:50.160 --> 38:51.150
So young.

38:51.160 --> 38:52.660
Young, my ass.

38:52.660 --> 38:56.650
I'm older than your girlfriend,
old man.

38:56.660 --> 38:58.150
Who do you think you are?

38:58.160 --> 39:00.330
Why are you hanging around
with a blind kid?

39:00.330 --> 39:03.000
I'm his older brother. 
What about it?

39:03.000 --> 39:03.830
Let's just go.

39:03.840 --> 39:05.170
Stay right there.

39:06.340 --> 39:10.000
Somebody disabled shouldn't
pretend to be normal.

39:10.010 --> 39:11.170
Hold on.

39:11.180 --> 39:12.840
What...?

39:12.850 --> 39:14.340
What did you say about 
"disabled"?

39:14.350 --> 39:15.510
If he can't see,

39:15.520 --> 39:17.850
he should go stand alone in a
corner.

39:17.850 --> 39:19.680
If you have eyes,

39:19.690 --> 39:21.180
watch out for people when
you're walking.

39:21.190 --> 39:22.850
Don't tell me your eyes...

39:22.860 --> 39:26.020
are only used to look at 
young girls?

39:29.200 --> 39:30.180
I told you to apologize.

39:30.200 --> 39:33.690
After you pay for your things, 
then apologize to my brother,

39:33.700 --> 39:35.030
old man.

39:35.030 --> 39:37.370
You fucker.

39:39.710 --> 39:41.700
Customer!

39:41.710 --> 39:43.370
Don't fight.

39:43.380 --> 39:44.880
<i>I barely touched him.</i>

39:44.880 --> 39:46.870
You all planned this, didn't you?

39:46.880 --> 39:47.540
What's going on?

39:47.550 --> 39:49.710
I just barely touched him.

39:49.720 --> 39:50.710
He seems seriously hurt.

39:50.720 --> 39:52.550
<i>I told you to let it go.</i>

39:52.550 --> 39:54.210
<i>He's all in a cold sweat.</i>

39:54.220 --> 39:55.720
<i>What to do?</i>

39:55.720 --> 39:57.880
Wait a second. Oh, my stomach...

39:57.890 --> 39:59.550
Are you all right?

40:02.900 --> 40:05.060
I really didn't mean to!

40:05.060 --> 40:06.570
It's just that he was...

40:06.570 --> 40:08.560
I just barely touched him!

40:08.570 --> 40:11.400
It really was his fault, making 
a scene about nothing!

40:11.400 --> 40:13.240
Please lower your voice.

40:13.240 --> 40:14.570
You should understand the
reason.

40:14.570 --> 40:16.410
That's his brother.

40:16.410 --> 40:18.740
He's disabled...

40:18.750 --> 40:20.240
Look.

40:20.250 --> 40:21.910
He has a physical disability.

40:21.920 --> 40:24.080
It's all my fault.

40:24.080 --> 40:25.740
I wanted to buy my brother
some clothes,

40:25.750 --> 40:29.090
so I forced him to go out.

40:35.260 --> 40:38.590
I only...

40:38.600 --> 40:43.590
want him to succeed in a world
full of prejudice. That's why I
brought him out!

40:46.110 --> 40:48.940
Unfortunately, there's so much
discrimination...

40:51.950 --> 40:53.440
It's all my fault.

40:55.280 --> 40:57.610
I'm sorry.

40:57.620 --> 41:00.610
It's all because of me.

41:00.620 --> 41:02.450
It must really hurt.

41:02.460 --> 41:04.790
I'm over here, you idiot!

41:04.790 --> 41:07.950
You're worried about me at a
time like this, you idiot?

41:13.970 --> 41:15.630
Come here.

41:15.640 --> 41:16.970
Okay.

41:36.660 --> 41:38.490
Just see if I don't get that guy!

41:38.490 --> 41:39.820
He was lucky.

41:39.830 --> 41:40.490
What are you doing?

41:40.490 --> 41:42.830
What do you mean?

41:42.830 --> 41:44.820
Are you going to academy
classes?

41:44.830 --> 41:48.320
Your acting was really great.

41:48.330 --> 41:49.670
I was keeping up with you.

41:49.670 --> 41:51.500
You little bastard.

41:51.500 --> 41:53.670
What do you mean calling me,
"you"?

41:53.670 --> 41:57.510
Then what should I call you?

41:57.510 --> 41:59.340
Do you think you're Hong Gil
Dong?

41:59.350 --> 42:04.010
You have a brother, but you 
can't call him your brother?

42:04.020 --> 42:06.510
"Hyeong", what bullshit.

42:06.520 --> 42:08.510
Even a dog passing by would 
laugh.

42:10.860 --> 42:13.350
You used to call me "hyeong".

